<sect2 id="Hbox"><title>Hbox</title>
<para>The <code>hbox</code> component is used to create a horizontally oriented box. Each component placed in the hbox will be placed horizontally in a row.</para>
<para/>
<para>
<graphic fileref="images/box.png"/>
</para>
<programlisting>&lt;zk&gt;&#13;    &lt;vbox&gt;&#13;        &lt;button label="Button 1"/&gt;&#13;        &lt;button label="Button 2"/&gt;&#13;    &lt;/vbox&gt;&#13;    &lt;hbox&gt;&#13;        &lt;button label="Button 3"/&gt;&#13;        &lt;button label="Button 4"/&gt;&#13;    &lt;/hbox&gt;&#13;&lt;/zk&gt;&#13;</programlisting><sect3><title>Class Name</title>
<para>
<code>org.zkoss.zul.Hbox</code>
